        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-5 gap-6 text-center">
        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-6 shadow-sm">
          <div class="text-3xl mb-2">ðŸ’¼</div>
